text: Aznashevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Tungatarovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 11 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 75 km from Uchaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Aznashevo
